%2Fi%2Fhhj5ZOd.jpg&h=de2e3bd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:33:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">天美人<br />\n上帝安排下凡 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">帶弓天美人，鄭字也</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">自西來，東嫁去<br />\n東方屬木<br />\n林字也</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><br />\n朝中日漸安<br />\n月字也<br />\n長弓在地<br />\n取其形 弓=D<br />\n同為月字</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">天美人自西來<br />\n朝中日漸安<br />\n<br />\n娥，字從女，從我，我亦聲。「我」本義是「兵器，執戈之人」，轉義為「王族」、「貴族」。「女」和「我」聯合起來表示「王族女子」、「貴族女子」</span>[/quote]"},{"pid":"edfe1e5bc91f0af4cfda9260a92d4e47c2443693","tid":1317831,"uid":241151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376afbd15a84d5a64f65619ad916837be8372a82","tid":1317831,"uid":241151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a749a1ff24339cfd8d5f74483c478c7fea29669","tid":1317831,"uid":256218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:57:33.000Z","msg":"其實推背圖已經唔準，因為所以卦象早被調亂，你睇緊果啲並唔係順序圖嚟"}]}